<TEXT>
robert polhill who used to talk of his love for his wifes 
native lebanon left that country a weakened man who said he kept 
his sanity during 39 months of captivity by staying angry at his 
captors 
i was angry at what was done to me at being taken away from 
my wife and family my friends and students the 55yearold 
