through meditation he said his followers could destroy the 
family the church and the state structures he said were 
destroying humanity 
he developed or synthesized several techniques including one in 
which followers jump up and down yelling hoo hoo hoo 
unlike gurus who demanded that disciples reject worldly goods 
rajneesh encouraged his followers to revel in sensual pleasures 
