<TEXT>
spring came for alfredo mustelier on march 21 
after two decades as a prisoner he was free 
free prison uniform meaning he had to live in his undershorts 
prisoners like mustelier who refuse the prison regimen are 
called plantados or steadfast ones they once were many but 
musteliers release left only two 
frustration and hopelessness so overwhelmed mustelier that he 
took out his rage on his teeth grinding them relentlessly some 
were reduced to half their normal size 
</TEXT>
</DOC>

