next month 
the robert m bass group decision was disclosed in a filing with 
the securities and exchange commission in washington 
the bass group which holds a 59 percent stake in the new 
yorkbased cosmetics company said it would vote in favor of 
submitting the companys poison pill defense to a shareholder 
vote bass group said it also supported a proposal seeking 
confidential voting for shareholders 
but the bass group said it would vote against a proposal to set 
up a shareholders advisory committee at the annual meeting in new 
york on may 3 
